<paragraph id="682736A5FF1BD4CCFF61F46BFDBFFA56" blockId="132.[151,1437,294,1511]" pageId="132" pageNumber="133">
<emphasis id="5AECEAB7FF1BD4CCFF61F46BFE83FACB" bold="true" box="[199,315,1374,1401]" pageId="132" pageNumber="133">Remarks.</emphasis>
In all Vietnamese papers it is cited as 
<emphasis id="5AECEAB7FF1BD4CCFD49F46BFC59FACA" box="[751,993,1374,1400]" italics="true" pageId="132" pageNumber="133">
<taxonomicName id="AF984D26FF1BD4CCFD49F46BFC38FACA" authorityName="Yosii" authorityYear="1966" box="[751,896,1374,1400]" class="Collembola" family="Dicyrtomidae" genus="Calvatomina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Symphypleona" pageId="132" pageNumber="133" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Calvatomina</taxonomicName>
antenna
</emphasis>
(Nguyen, 1995), but this species is not described in Nguyễn T.T. (1995c) and had only been described in Nguyen’s thesis (Nguyễn T.T. 1994) (nomen nu- dum). The first time the species is described in an official publication is in Nguyễn T.T. (2017), therefore the correct authorship is Nguyễn T.T., 2017.
</paragraph>
